Subject: drm/amd/display: Fix Coverity INTERGER_OVERFLOW within
 construct_integrated_info
Git-commit: 176abbcc71952e23009a6ed194fd203b99646884
Patch-mainline: v6.11-rc1
References: jsc#PED-9898 jsc#PED-10191 jsc#PED-10197 jsc#PED-10226 jsc#PED-10237 jsc#PED-10340 jsc#PED-10852 jsc#PED-11022 stable-fixes

[Why]
For substrcation, coverity reports integer overflow
warning message when variable type is uint32_t.

[How]
Change varaible type to int32_t.

